features.text:
Bittrees is a metaverse native company that services virtual spaces and empowers artistic communities  through the use of technology and automation. 

The Bittrees Portal network helps adventurers travel across the growing cryptovoxels ecosystem. Click on any Bittrees logo to visit the hub.

We see the metaverse as a mirror of the physical world where the only limit is the imagination. Cryptovoxels is part of that foundation. Welcome to the digital revolution.

Feel free to reach out anytime! We are collaborating with designers, architects, artists, and anyone else who wants to invest in the future of creative thought.

-jh mar2020
Yield Farming in DeFi: Earn, Contribute and Learn
